Questions:
What should you do if you decide to withdraw from the pancreatic cancer study early?
A) Inform the study team immediately and discuss any potential risks with your doctor;
B) Stop taking the study medication without notifying anyone;
C) Continue taking the study medication until it runs out;
D) Wait until the study is completed before informing the study team of your decision to withdraw.

Correct answer: A) Inform the study team immediately and discuss any potential risks with your doctor;
